  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink69-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">talaimakaṉ petumpaip paruvattāḷ oru parattaiyaik kaḷavil maṇantu
          oḻukukiṉṟataṉai aṟinta talaimakaḷ taṉakku illai eṉṟu avaṉ maṟaittuḻic colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink69">
        <lg type="edition" style="pūṭṭuvil">
          <l>kaṇṭaṉe mallamō makiḻnaniṉ peṇṭē</l>
          <l>palarāṭu peruntuṟai malaroṭu vanta</l>
          <l>taṇpuṉal vaṇṭa luytteṉa</l>
          <l>vuṇkaṇ civappa vaḻutuniṉ ṟōḷē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> We saw your woman, did we not, o delightful man? </l>
          <l> Crying on your shoulder until her kohl-rimmed eyes turned red, </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> because the cool flood, </l>
          <l rend="indent4"> coming along with blossoms</l>
          <l rend="indent6"> into the big ghat where many bathe,</l>
          <l rend="indent8"> washed away her sand castles. </l>


        </lg>


      </div>
    </body>
